    <h1>Project 0 — Overview</h1>
    <p class="meta">Goal: Build intuition for how distance to subject and focal length affect perspective and the center of projection.</p>

    <h2>Part 1 — Selfie: Wrong vs Right</h2>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <figure>
        <img src="./media/part1_close.jpg" alt="Close selfie—wide angle distortion" />
