      </figure>
      <figure>
        <img src="./media/part1_zoom.jpg" alt="Stepped back and zoomed—more natural proportions" />
        <figcaption>Step back + zoom — proportions look more natural.</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <h2>Part 2 — Architectural Perspective Compression</h2>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <figure>
        <img src="./media/part2_zoom.jpg" alt="Zoomed street view—compressed perspective" />
        <figcaption>Zoomed from far away — scene appears flattened/compressed.</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure>
        <img src="./media/part2_wide.jpg" alt="Closer wide view—exaggerated depth" />
        <figcaption>Closer, no zoom — stronger sense of depth.</figcaption>
      </figure>
